mysql5.7 远程可以连接，本地命令行连接不上
删除mysql.sock.lock


show grants;

flush privileges;

mysql删除binlog日志
PURGE MASTER LOGS TO 'mysql_bin.000060';


其它关于查看死锁的命令：

1：查看当前的事务
SELECT * FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.INNODB_TRX;

2：查看当前锁定的事务

SELECT * FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.INNODB_LOCKS;

3：查看当前等锁的事务
SELECT * FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.INNODB_LOCK_WAITS;